<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̉nt fy ḍʿfy qwty ạ̉nt fy fqry tẖrwty wḥdk tkfyny
 ḥbk ly jwhrty ʿnhạ lạ ln ạstgẖny wḥdk tkfyny
 ʿny ạ̉kẖdẖt ṣlyby mt wqmt ltḥyyny wḥdk tkfyny
 ḥynmạ ạ̉sqṭ trfʿny wmn ḥbk tgẖmrny wḥdk tkfyny
 yswʿ ạbn ạllh ạsmk qdws
 You are my strength when I am weak
 You are my treasure that I seek
 You are my all in all
 Seeking you as a precious jewel
 Lord to give up I'd be a fool
 Taking my sin my cross my shame
 Rising again I bless your name
 You are my all in all
 When I fall down you pick me up
 When I am dry you fill my cup
 You are my all in all
 Jesus Lamb of God worthy is your name</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉nt tkfyny</title>
</song>